summary: SummaryMaybelline Colossal Bubble Washable Mascara delivers buildable inflated volume with sleek separation. Inflator comb brush and lash inflating formula inflate 100% of lashes.
details: DetailsFeaturesBuildable, sleek volume, bubbling up one lash at a time. Colossal Bubble Mascara by Maybelline allows you to inflate your lashes with bold impact in a New York minute.This long-lasting mascara leaves lashes looking separated and feeling light.Meet Colossal Bubbleâ€™s breakthrough inflator comb brush. The spiral shape with deep-cut bristles will inflate lashes from root to tip for separated, sleek lashes that last.The Colossal Bubble lash inflating formula inflates every lash for a voluminous bubble-like look and feel. This buildable and lightweight formula goes on smooth and easily, leaving you with separated, sleek lashes.BenefitsMaybelline mascara is allergy testedOpthalmologist testedSuitable for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearersRemoves easilyItem 2639784How To UseFor best results, hold inflator comb brush against lashes and extend from root to tip repeatedly until desired look is achieved.IngredientsAqua / Water / Eau, Behenyl Behenate, Acrylates Copolymer, Cetearyl Alcohol, Stearic Acid, Palmitic Acid, Poly C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate, Butylene Glycol, Pvp, Vp/Eicosene Copolymer, Aminomethyl Propanediol, Kaolin, Phenoxyethanol, Caprylyl Glycol, Pentylene Glycol, Potassium Cetyl Phosphate, Myristic Acid, Silica, May Contain: CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499 / Iron Oxides, CI 77007 / Ultramarines, CI 77742 / Manganese Violet, Mica, CI 77891 / Titanium Dioxide]. faceoff_positive.comments:
[I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I recently tried the Maybelline Colossal Bubble Washable Mascara, and I have to say, it's been a pleasant surprise. The unique "bubble" brush design caught my attentionâ€”it has a spiral shape with deep-cut bristles that separate and volumize each lash. The brush did a good job of coating my lashes evenly, providing a noticeable lift and volume without clumping.

The formula feels lightweight, which is great for everyday wear. I appreciated that it didn't flake or smudge throughout the day, even during longer hours. However, I did notice that it takes a bit longer to dry, so it's best to avoid blinking too much right after application to prevent any smudging.

One of the best features for me was how easily it washed off at the end of the day. A gentle cleanser was sufficient to remove it completely, which is a plus compared to some mascaras that require more effort to take off. That said, if you're someone with very straight or hard-to-curl lashes, you might find that this mascara doesn't hold a curl as effectively as some others. It provides volume and definition, but the curl-holding power could be better for certain lash types.

Overall, the Maybelline Colossal Bubble Washable Mascara is a great choice for those looking for a mascara that offers volume and easy removal. It's especially great for everyday use when you want your lashes to look fuller without the hassle of a complicated removal process.
faceoff_positive.headline: Thickens and separates

faceoff_negative.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This mascara contains less ingredients than I expected, but I don't think they're great. The very dark black color is fine. However, the spiral brush tip causes problems with the amount of mascara that comes out. Even with getting as much of the excess off of the brush as I could, the mascara was still quite sticky and clumped together. Unfortunately, I really didn't see any added volume from the inflator comb brush either. After I wore it for less than an hour, when I wasn't in a hot or humid environment, the mascara dried out and flaked off my eyelashes. I ended up with little black dots all over my cheeks. This has been one of the oddest experiences that I've ever had with an eye makeup product because it clumped and flaked. Sadly, other than the sort of locking cap on the tube, the ease of removal and being washable is the best feature of this mascara.
faceoff_negative.headline: Got clumpy and flaked
